Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.83,TS-Manual,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\fay-0.08\fax0.5\fs28\fscy140\pos(708,372)}Manual
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢親の目から見ても そうでしたし
Dialogue: 9,0:04:30.30,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have always seen that in you,\Nand Tomiko-sama agreed with us.
